{"tid":1104943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墮樓小學女教師設靈 家人失望批教育局卸責","createTime":"2019-04-13T13:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T13:38:31.000Z","uid":215574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"248624e34ea3a503dff44cf592e7065c0eb3034b","tid":1104943,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h6KImF2q4aWR0FEOymQsWM05CagtHeHpnECI4eyt6N1ALdy5mSXcvVVYTMFQJcS46HXEvAlQSclVRcHozTnAv/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h6KImF2q4aWR0FEOymQsWM05CagtHeHpnECI4eyt6N1ALdy5mSXcvVVYTMFQJcS46HXEvAlQSclVRcHozTnAv%2Fw644&h=38931d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天水圍東華三院李東海小學女教師林麗棠，疑難抵工作壓力，上月6日在校內墮樓身亡，並於今日在紅磡萬國殯儀館設靈。靈堂以白色為主調，中央放置林老師遺照，並掛上「教澤永懷」的橫額。教育局局長楊潤雄、東華三院主席蔡榮星、前主席王賢誌亦先後到場鞠躬致意。<br />\n<br />\n林麗棠的妹妹表示，多謝各界連日來的關心，並指在事件發生後，收到多名林老師生前的好友、同事、學生及家長的慰問。她又指，對於姐姐的離世感到難過，並指「呢個幾月對我哋嚟講真係好漫長，依然好掛住佢，但我哋會努力走出傷痛」。她亦指，感謝王賢誌及東華三院就事件所成立的獨立委員會的付出及關注，亦看到委員會上眾人的誠意。然而，她指委員會一直未有交代具體的調查時間表，並指「我哋唔知仲要等幾耐，又或者仲應唔應該等落去」。<br />\n<br />\n林麗棠的弟弟則指，對教育局的表現感失望，直斥「教育局一直匿埋喺辦學團體後面，無作出任何負責任的嘅行為」。他亦指，教育局僅稱要等待東華三院獨立調查委員會的調查報告再作研究。他認為，教育局需自行作出調查，並了解東華三院的調查進度及方向等，亦需討論現時的政策及校董成員代表性是否恰當。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，「校本機制根本就係畀教育局推卸責任的籍口」，並指老師的工作環境及態度，直接影響學生的成長及學習，認為局方應更有責任心。另外，他們亦指，事發至今仍未能接觸小學校長羅婉儀，並指希望能親自聆聽羅婉儀的說法。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hbZCxaRnrPXV-ARejkwtCIkRXPhpNbS52GjdsaiFvY0EBYnp3Q2MnRFwBZxJSOXorF2R7EVgHJkRbZS4iRGIn/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hbZCxaRnrPXV-ARejkwtCIkRXPhpNbS52GjdsaiFvY0EBYnp3Q2MnRFwBZxJSOXorF2R7EVgHJkRbZS4iRGIn%2Fw644&h=28fe07ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林麗棠的妹妹(左)表示，多謝各界連日來的關心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hCFpt-U1sHGlNDTa_oPNjPndbHwZ-YQ9qKTtNdhJjQl0ybltrcDtbWG5fEF80Pls3I2NbDW4MB1hoaQ8-d2Nb/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hCFpt-U1sHGlNDTa_oPNjPndbHwZ-YQ9qKTtNdhJjQl0ybltrcDtbWG5fEF80Pls3I2NbDW4MB1hoaQ8-d2Nb%2Fw644&h=24eedae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林麗棠今日在紅磡萬國殯儀館設靈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hmTl8YWZ2MntRQRitvNNNLGsXMRRiLSF4NXdjZA4vbE8uInV5bHV5SnITaxx_I3UlPy91GnVIKUp0JSEsa3R5/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hmTl8YWZ2MntRQRitvNNNLGsXMRRiLSF4NXdjZA4vbE8uInV5bHV5SnITaxx_I3UlPy91GnVIKUp0JSEsa3R5%2Fw644&h=8bb368c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林麗棠的弟弟(右)則指，對教育局的表現感失望。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hTkbiIoR0C0RfECGSsrF0E2dGCCtsfBhHOyZaWwB-VXAgc0xGYiFDdXwTBSEmckwaMX5CKz8RXSAmIUpGZA/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hTkbiIoR0C0RfECGSsrF0E2dGCCtsfBhHOyZaWwB-VXAgc0xGYiFDdXwTBSEmckwaMX5CKz8RXSAmIUpGZA%2Fw644&h=bb98b440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林麗棠今日在紅磡萬國殯儀館設靈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h9bT3Sq3UZk1pSkybhRYZGlAcZSJaJnVODXw3UjYkOHkWKSFPVS16fEpObS5NfiETByQsKkkPOXUQLiAdAn8/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h9bT3Sq3UZk1pSkybhRYZGlAcZSJaJnVODXw3UjYkOHkWKSFPVS16fEpObS5NfiETByQsKkkPOXUQLiAdAn8%2Fw644&h=1ad0ae73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東華三院前主席王賢誌亦到場鞠躬致意。<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E8%A8%AD%E9%9D%88+%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B%E6%89%B9%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%8D%B8%E8%B2%AC-jWOVLr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E9%259D%2588%2B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%259C%259B%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%258D%25B8%25E8%25B2%25AC-jWOVLr&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=e5abdcb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E8%A8%AD%E9%9D%88+%